author: ArkahmAsylym
title: Great Promo for Christmas Season!
review: This Reindeer is so cute!  Very simple to put together, it is a great promotional item to hang on the Christmas Tree.  The big eyes and simple to assemble antlers make this ornament adorable. Great job LEGO. My only other suggestion would been to have put an alternate red button nose in the set so the owner could have made a Rudolf out of it.
